title: CD UP Manica
text: Clube Desportivo Universidade Pedagógica de Manica is a <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club based in Gondola (near <a href="Chimoio">Chimoio</a>), <a href="Manica%20Province">Manica Province</a>, <a href="Mozambique">Mozambique</a>, which currently competes in the <a href="Mo%C3%A7ambola">Moçambola</a>. UP Manica was promoted after winning the 2017 Moçambola 2 (Center Zone) championship, and the club's first season in the top level of Mozambican football will begin in 2018.
